    "description": "<strong>在石油大亨模拟器游戏中建造并运营好石油钻井平台!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/1f681f2cb66b032bceede44b59105de1.poster.avif?t=1726695618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/1f681f2cb66b032bceede44b59105de1.webm?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/1f681f2cb66b032bceede44b59105de1.mp4?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>踏上这段有趣的冒险之旅，建起属于你的石油钻井平台! 从一个小小的钻井平台起步，逐步发展成一个大型的全方位开采平台综合体! 不断完善平台的搭建和运营，以提高生产效率和增加现金流，同时让你的员工足够感受到工作的快乐和安全!<br><br><strong>建立公司良好的声誉!/b]<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/6eded3053a9cb36a080f0b3f12f2ce57.poster.avif?t=1726695618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/6eded3053a9cb36a080f0b3f12f2ce57.webm?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/6eded3053a9cb36a080f0b3f12f2ce57.mp4?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>签订长期合同，售出你的产品。不断开拓新的市场。管理好你在市场中的声誉和维护好客户关系，同时尽力提高收益!<br><br><strong>遇到许多独特的事件及场景</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/3e7bfa5e8b0e6e1ff754606df28c6ec8.poster.avif?t=1726695618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/3e7bfa5e8b0e6e1ff754606df28c6ec8.webm?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/3e7bfa5e8b0e6e1ff754606df28c6ec8.mp4?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在环境危机期间管理好平台的运转。面对无数的挑战和威胁，比如：暴雪、风暴、火灾，等等！时刻不要忘记，你有责任保护你的钻井人员免受贪婪的海盗、恐怖分子甚至是致命疾病的袭击和侵扰！<br><br><strong>管理好石油钻井工作团队</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/2574535343c2297e42be0fb7a67ca413.poster.avif?t=1726695618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/2574535343c2297e42be0fb7a67ca413.webm?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/2574535343c2297e42be0fb7a67ca413.mp4?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>任人唯贤地选用人员。多留意他们具备的各种技能以及对他们的统计数据。注意他们对工作的满意度和生活质量如何。随着平台的发展，打造您的游戏玩法并为您的员工提供一个更好的家。能力合格和高满意度的员工是提高生产力的关键！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/7e4f7a5c28ebc49de2982f33a0751a40.poster.avif?t=1726695618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/7e4f7a5c28ebc49de2982f33a0751a40.webm?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083300/extras/7e4f7a5c28ebc49de2982f33a0751a40.mp4?t=1726695618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在世界的不同角落探索各种有趣的场景。从冰天雪地的北极，到海盗横行的热带海域，再到鬼混出没的孤岛。<br><strong>快来石油大亨的游戏世界开始探险吧!</strong></strong>",
